# npm shrinkwrap — DaloyJS publishes via pnpm with `frozen-lockfile=true`
# and `verify-store-integrity=true`; an `npm-shrinkwrap.json` checked in
# here would silently override that posture for anyone installing
# `@daloyjs/core` via plain `npm install`. Enforced at CI by
# `pnpm verify:no-shrinkwrap` (Socket npm-shrinkwrap gate).
